Thank you very much! Bigrod!rnrnDo you guys know a secret? you can print out the charts to a PDF file. Simply go to C:\\ProgramData\\Jeppesen\\Common\\Fonts , classificate by type, then install the first 4 TTF fonts, just select them, right click and install (or install as shortcut works too). Now you can save the charts in pdf, bring with you anywhere, and print when needed, hope you guys enjoy my tip! regards
